{{!
    @template block_culcourse_listing/info

    CUL Course Listing Course Box Info template.

    The purpose of this template is to render ...

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * 
        * 
